title: Make This Brand New 1 Bedroom In Unique Historic Building Yours Today!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Enjoy modern living at Millworks Lofts where you will find luxurious features and amenities at an affordable price!', 'Located on Hiawatha in the Longfellow neighborhood of Minneapolis, Millworks is conveniently located near Downtown Minneapolis and the MSP Airport.', 'Just steps from your door you have access to public transportation that will take you anywhere in the cities you desire.', 'The community is surrounded by a charming neighborhood that is filled with family-owned stores and restaurants.', 'Millworks Lofts features spacious floorplans with modern finishes like stainless steel appliances and quartz kitchen counter tops.', 'It also has amazing amenities like a rooftop deck and geothermal heating.', 'Don’t miss out on this great opportunity and apply online today!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Pet-friendly community', '- Restored original historic windows (Select Homes)', '- Exposed brick walls', '- Quartz countertops', '- Private balcony or patio* (Select Homes)', '- Modern, polished concrete flooring throughout', '- Washer & dryer in EVERY apartment home', "- 12' - 14' foot ceilings", 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Millworks Lofts participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Wednesday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to schedule your tour:', 'show contact info', 'Millworks Lofts', '4041 Hiawatha Avenue South', 'Minneapolis, MN, 55406', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'g881U7GrF7gA']
